{"tid":1476084,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"兌美金定拎港幣","createTime":"2019-08-15T16:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T04:24:18.000Z","uid":60066,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"3b22f8ba99fb152d893f6d90c612120675425196","tid":1476084,"uid":60066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:36:33.000Z","msg":"本身諗住兌美金，之後見到啲post一啲話兌美金，一啲話拎港紙<br />\n<br />\n 其實兩者唔係會有互相抵消嘅作用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利申乜鳩都唔識<br />\n<br />\n睇完啲解釋大概理解為拎港紙就係由銀行拎港幣現金出嚟，兌美金就係將港紙放返去再拎美金出嚟<br />\n<br />\n咁其實聽日係要做邊樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到好撚亂"},{"pid":"c65526b77fdab6333294f0d49b28b0e17fe17200","tid":1476084,"uid":60066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:36:52.000Z","msg":"想有人解釋下"},{"pid":"7be542e21a37ba535323dfb372250565fa2e9d3a","tid":1476084,"uid":60066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:37:12.000Z","msg":"平時最多去旅行撳三四千蚊美金出嚟"},{"pid":"268e9a6bd66910fd94f177652e80046f76970021","tid":1476084,"uid":60066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:37:23.000Z","msg":"今次真係完全唔撚明"},{"pid":"2d0c0ea03baa3b3b87e436f8cb0b0f1c991ef379","tid":1476084,"uid":60066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:37:52.000Z","msg":"雖然聽日都唔知銀行會唔會有美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a010d070e323d083283d6d956b938cc251e65b","tid":1476084,"uid":60066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:38:05.000Z","msg":"不過都真係想理解一下"},{"pid":"3e942614409ae52065544bd7184b2de67ee87ec4","tid":1476084,"uid":182822,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:38:32.000Z","msg":"無論兌美金定拎港紙只要用阿婆儲錢法就得"},{"pid":"bab6dd82b18c3b12b9d93dff5fafc6e05a712a05","tid":1476084,"uid":60066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:39:11.000Z","msg":"陣間人人拎港紙， 原來我兌美金係會搞到大家就唔好"},{"pid"